<li><a href="/wiki/Hans_Peter_Luhn" title="Hans Peter Luhn">Hans Peter Luhn</a></li>
<li><a href="http://ciir.cs.umass.edu/personnel/croft.html" class="external text" title="http://ciir.cs.umass.edu/personnel/croft.html" rel="nofollow">W. Bruce Croft</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Karen_Sp%C3%A4rck_Jones" title="Karen Spärck Jones">Karen Spärck Jones</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/C._J._van_Rijsbergen" title="C. J. van Rijsbergen">C. J. van Rijsbergen</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.soi.city.ac.uk/~ser/homepage.html" class="external text" title="http://www.soi.city.ac.uk/~ser/homepage.html" rel="nofollow">Stephen E. Robertson</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Martin_Porter" title="Martin Porter">Martin Porter</a></li>
</ul>
